      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Subject: Your Application for the Senior Developer Position\n\nDear [Candidate's Name],\n\nThank you for your interest in the Senior Developer position at [Company Name] and for your enthusiasm during the interview process. We appreciate the time and effort you invested in sharing your skills and experiences with us.\n\nWe were particularly impressed by your system design skills and your positive attitude. Your ability to articulate complex concepts with clarity and your passion for software development truly shone through during our discussions. We believe that your expertise in this area is a valuable asset, and we wish you the best of luck in your future endeavors.\n\nAfter careful consideration, we have decided to move forward with another candidate whose qualifications and experience more closely align with our current needs, specifically in the area of Kubernetes. While we felt that this candidate's experience would be a better fit for our current project requirements, we wanted to acknowledge the strengths you brought to our team.\n\nWe encourage you to apply for future opportunities that match your qualifications and to keep an eye on our career page for new openings. We believe that your skills and enthusiasm will lead you to great success in your career.\n\nThank you once again for your interest in [Company Name].\n\nBest regards,\n[Your Name]\n[Your Position]\n[Company Name",
